VERSION  FEATURES
=======  ======================================================================
V0.1     Code tested using a single GPU on the Bracewell cluster. 
         Tagged on July 11, 2017. 
         Separate kernels for Q and U.
         Input cubes are processed frame-by-frame.
V0.2     Code tested using a single GPU on the Bracewell cluster.
         Tagged on July 25, 2017.
         Q, U, and P dirty maps are processed in one kernel.
         Each line of sight is processed separately.
V0.3     Code tested using a single GPU on the Bracewell cluster.
         Tagged on August 11, 2017.
         Supports both HDF5 and FITS input data formats.
         FITS input cubes must be rotated such that the freq axis is axis1.
===============================================================================
